Create CallableCode object

callable_code.Rd

Create CallableCode object to execute specific code and get reproducible call.

callable_code(code)

Arguments

code

(character)
a string containing R code to reproduce the desired object. Please be aware that objects assigned to temporary environment are locked which means that they can't be modified.

Value

CallableCode object

Examples

cf <- callable_code(code = "mtcars")
cf$run()
